            <title>RX-78-2 元祖高達發光擺設，還原度高+造工精細+有新鮮感</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/01/rx-78-2/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=rx-78-2</link>
