            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1200285</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">機動戰士高達系列向來推出都頗受歡迎。Bandai 最新推出的 Bandai BN GUNDAM HEAD COLLECTION vol 1 RX 78 2 高達頭部模型，售 1,299.9 港元，可説非常抵玩，初步上手感覺很有份量，新鮮感一流。事不宜遲，馬上開箱評測！</p><p><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="size-medium wp-image-1200322 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09013-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09013-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09013-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09013-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09013-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09013-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Bandai BN GUNDAM HEAD COLLECTION vol 1 RX 78 2 高達頭部模型</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">剛推出的 Bandai BN GUNDAM HEAD COLLECTION vol 1 RX 78 2 高達頭部模型，包裝盒都幾大盒，畢竟也是大大個真人尺寸高達頭部模型。打開包裝後有 2 個部份，包括 1 份説明書、1 份水貼、由 1 盒發泡膠包裝的本體及 1 層配件及 10 cm 高的底座。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1200317 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09030-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09030-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09030-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09030-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09030-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09030-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲水貼</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1200319 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09007-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09007-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09007-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09007-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09007-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09007-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲底座</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200316 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08987-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08987-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08987-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08987-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08987-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08987-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲本體</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>模型大過頭，細節位有誠意</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">高達頭部模型本體高 37 cm 闊 49 cm 深 33 cm，目測比真人頭部的尺寸更大。像真度高，頗忠實地還原元祖高達頭部，細節位置絕對有誠意。天線與本體是分開的，跟著説明書安裝就可以了，相信難不到高達迷。質感方面，雖然模型大部份是使用了塑料製造，但小編覺得質感不錯，有金屬感，同時有一定重量。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200323 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09020-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09020-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09020-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09020-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09020-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09020-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲模型目測比真人頭部的尺寸更大</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200324 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08999-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08999-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08999-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08999-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08999-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08999-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲像真度高，頗忠實地還原元祖高達頭部</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200325 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09008-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09008-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09008-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09008-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09008-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09008-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲天線與本體是分開的，跟著説明書安裝就可以了</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200347 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08988-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08988-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08988-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08988-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08988-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08988-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200345 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08989-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08989-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08989-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08989-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08989-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08989-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200326 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08991-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08991-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08991-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08991-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08991-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08991-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200327 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08990-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08990-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08990-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08990-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08990-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08990-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200329 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08992-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08992-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08992-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08992-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08992-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08992-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲細節位置絕對有誠意，有金屬感</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>3 個發光位置，需自行買電池</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">高達頭部模型共有 3 個發光位置，分別是 1 對眼及頭部前後端監視器。裝上電池的步驟很簡單，首先打開模型頂部深灰色部份，再用螺絲批開啟電池槽，用家要準備 3 粒 AA 電池（模型包裝未有提供電池），然後蓋上蓋子，再啟動開關，3 個發光位置就會著燈了。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200330 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09003-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09003-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09003-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09003-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09003-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09003-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲首先打開模型頂部深灰色部份</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200331 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09004-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09004-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09004-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09004-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09004-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09004-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲再用螺絲批開啟電池槽</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200332 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09005-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09005-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09005-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09005-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09005-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09005-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲準備 3 粒 AA 電池</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200333 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09006-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09006-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09006-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09006-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09006-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09006-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200338 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09000-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09000-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09000-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09000-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09000-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09000-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200339 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09001-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09001-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09001-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09001-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09001-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09001-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200340 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09002-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09002-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09002-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09002-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09002-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09002-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲啟動開關，3 個發光位置就會著燈了</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>不建議戴上頭上</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">相信很多高達迷都關心模型可否戴上頭上，答案是可能可以，但小編不建議。要戴上頭上先要拆除所有底部螺絲，但螺絲上得比較實，加上模型裏面有電線，而底部空間未必人人都能夠通過，基於總總考量，小編一律不建議戴上頭上。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200334 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09009-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09009-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09009-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09009-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09009-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09009-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200336 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09011-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09011-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09011-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09011-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09011-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09011-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲要戴上頭上先要拆除所有底部螺絲，但螺絲上得比較實</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200337 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09029-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09029-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09029-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09029-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09029-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09029-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲底部空間未必人人都能夠通過，小編一律不建議戴上頭上</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>總結：還原度高，造工細緻</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">Bandai BN GUNDAM HEAD COLLECTION vol 1 RX 78 2 高達頭部模型造工精緻，幾乎所有在影視作品中出現的細節位都有呈現出來，還原度高。著燈部份亦見心思，不只是亮燈，監視器和眼睛裏的紋路亦有造好。整體來説 RX 78 2 高達頭部模型完成度高，夠新鮮感，絕對值得高達迷收藏。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200348 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09018-2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09018-2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09018-2-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09018-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09018-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN09018-2-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200341 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08994-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08994-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08994-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08994-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08994-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/KAN08994-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1200342 aligncenter" src="https://